        <extension url="urn:poc:discharge-summary">
          <valueString value="Ms. Fitzgerald admitted in septic shock secondary to E. coli urosepsis. Managed in MICU with norepinephrine (weaned off HD4), levofloxacin + gentamicin (adjusted to levofloxacin monotherapy after sensitivities). AKI resolved (Cr 1.9 at discharge). Coagulopathy resolved. Lactate cleared within 12 hours. Warfarin restarted HD6. Discharged to SNF." />
